Package org.newsclub.net.unix

Class EndOfFileJavaTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.newsclub.net.unix.EndOfFileTest
      • org.newsclub.net.unix.EndOfFileJavaTest
  • public class EndOfFileJavaTest
extends EndOfFileTest
    This test ensures that the test cases written for the junixsocket also pass for the standard Java Internet sockets. If they do not, the tests may be incorrect. As much as possible, junixsocket's AFUnixSocket should emulate the regular Java Internet sockets so they can be used with all existing tools. See http://code.google.com/p/junixsocket/issues/detail?id=9
    Author:
    Derrick Rice (April, 2010)
